      "filename": "Chapter 09_Love_Marriage_Relations",
      "content": "# 🌌 KAMA: LOVE, MARRIAGE & PARTNERSHIPS\n\n**MODULE:** RELATIONSHIP DYNAMICS & KULA (FAMILY)\n**STATUS:** EXPANDED GOD MODE (INTEGRATED LIBRARY)\n\n### 1. THE 7TH HOUSE: THE MIRROR (Yuvati)\n**Bhava 7 (Yuvati):** Spouse, Partners, Public Image, Open Enemies, 'The Other.'\n* **God Mode Logic:** The 7th is the furthest point from the Lagna (Self). It represents the psychological void we try to fill. We marry what we are *not*. It represents the 'Sunset' of the ego.\n\n### 2. D9 NAVAMSHA ANALYSIS (The Fruit of Marriage)\nThe D1 7th House is 'Marriage in General.' The D9 7th House is 'The Specific Spouse' and the *internal* quality of the bond.\n* **D1 7th Lord in D9:** If it falls in D9 6, 8, or 12 house, the marriage brings debt, conflict, or loss/separation, regardless of D1 strength.\n* **Darakaraka (DK):** The Jaimini indicator (lowest degree planet). Locate the DK in D9. This is the soul-significator of the partner.\n\n### 4. KUJA DOSHA (The Martian Flaw)\nMars in 1, 2, 4, 7, 8, 12 causes Kuja Dosha (Manglik). It creates aggression, heat, and potential early death/separation of spouse.\n* **Cancellation Logic:** Counter-Mars in partner's chart, Mars in Own/Exalted sign, Jupiter aspect, or Age > 28-30.\n\n### 5. KP MARRIAGE SCRIPT (The Event Trigger)\nTo predict outcomes, check the Cusp Sub Lord (CSL) and Dasha Significators.\n* **Marriage Promise:** **2, 7, 11** (Family, Bond, Gain).\n* **Divorce / Separation:** **1, 6, 10** (The Anti-Marriage Group; 12th from 2/7/11).\n* **The CSL Veto:** If the 7th Cusp Sub Lord signifies **4, 6, 10** (Separative) and has NO connection to 2, 7, 11, the native will *never* marry, even if the Dasha is favorable.\n\n### 7. DELAYED MARRIAGE (The Saturn Filter)\nMarriage is delayed if Saturn aspects 7th House or 7th Lord. Timing depends on Saturn and Jupiter *both* aspecting the 7th House/Lord in Transit (Double Transit Theory).\n\n### 10. TIMING OF MARRIAGE (The Clock)\nMarriage is likely during Dasha of 7th Lord, planet in 7th, Venus/Jupiter, or Darakaraka. Transit Jupiter must connect to 7th House/Lord."
