      "filename": "Chapter 10_Medical_Health_Arishta",
      "content": "# 🌌 ROGA & ARISHTA: HEALTH & LONGEVITY\n\n**MODULE:** MEDICAL ASTROLOGY & CRISIS\n**STATUS:** EXPANDED GOD MODE (INTEGRATED LIBRARY)\n\n### 1. THE PATHOLOGY OF HOUSES (Bhava Roga)\n* **Bhava 6 (Ari):** Disease, Debt, Enemies, Accidents. It is an **Upachaya** house. Malefics thrive here (immunity).\n* **Bhava 8 (Randhra):** Longevity, Surgery, Chronic Illness. The 'Black Swan' generator.\n* **Bhava 12 (Vyaya):** Hospitalization, Confinement. Connection of 6th Lord with 12th = Hospitalization.\n\n### 2. ARISHTA YOGAS (The Warning System)\n* **Balarishta:** Applies to charts < 12 years old. Moon in 6/8/12 aspected by Malefics is critical.\n* **Kemadruma Yoga:** Moon has no planets in 2nd or 12th from it (excluding Sun) and no aspect. Result: Deep loneliness, anxiety, mental frailty.\n\n### 3. DIAGNOSTIC SYSTEM (Planet = Tissue)\nIdentify the **Weakest Planet** and the **Afflicted Sign**.\n* **Sun:** Bones, Heart, Stomach, Right Eye, Vitality.\n* **Moon:** Blood, Body Fluids, Lungs, Left Eye, Breast, Mind.\n* **Mars:** Marrow, Muscles, Neck, Blood Pressure, Injury/Cuts.\n* **Mercury:** Skin, Nerves, Brain, Speech, Ears.\n* **Jupiter:** Fat, Liver, Ears, Memory, Intestines.\n* **Venus:** Semen/Ovaries, Face, Eyes, Kidneys, Glands.\n* **Saturn:** Nerves (Chronic), Legs, Teeth, Bones, Joints.\n* **Rahu:** Poisons, Leprosy, Cancer, Undiagnosable, Phobias.\n* **Ketu:** Viral, Epidemic, Itch, Cuts, Surgery.\n\n### 4. KP HEALTH SCRIPTS (Timing Disease)\n* **Good Health/Cure:** **1, 5, 11**.\n* **Disease Onset:** **6, 8, 12**.\n* **Surgery:** **8, 12** connected with **Mars** (Cutting).\n* **Death (Maraka):** **2, 7** (Primary Killers) + **Badhaka** + **12**.\n\n### 8. MRITYU BHAGA (The Death Degrees)\nCertain degrees are fatal. A planet located here (e.g., Moon in 26° Aries) destroys its signification. If the Dasha Lord is in Mrityu Bhaga, it causes severe health crises or death-like suffering."
